{"tid":344023,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"(mobile game) 有冇巴絲有興趣一齊寫game?","createTime":"2017-08-02T03:07:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T08:49:12.000Z","uid":68496,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"81816ce2fd5ab04cfeaac0a98cb8c024f9d45d39","tid":344023,"uid":68496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T03:07:52.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我同幾個朋友係大約一年前開始寫緊隻mobile game, 但係做落發現唔夠人手（因為大家都係part time做，但都做得7788，預計好快出街）有冇巴絲有冇興趣加入一齊繼續做？宜家我地團隊差：<br />\n<br />\nbackend developer (urgent)<br />\nClient side developer (urgent, c++, cocos 2d-x)<br />\nGraphic designer<br />\nIOS developer<br />\n<br />\n有興趣可以tg再講details<br />\nTg: mobilegamehk<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1b6de0f4623349fd41cc69834981ed48e5ce71f","tid":344023,"uid":68496,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T03:18:41.000Z","msg":"Sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔記得講，隻game係類似sim city類型，但係會同一般mobile game玩法上有幾大嘅分別（叫做多少少創新嘅元素<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）"},{"pid":"1b985a6795ba9af6bc6bc602c57ab6ad3c56cf6e","tid":344023,"uid":117901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T03:21:03.000Z","msg":"揾part time定full time?paid/unpaid?"},{"pid":"4a6e1928a2942674e9710db89be2fa57d649238f","tid":344023,"uid":68496,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T03:31:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>揾part time定full time?paid/unpaid?</blockquote><br />\n暫時係part time, 同埋會係合作/分股形式（我地幾個都比左筆錢出黎，又係窮jj，真係請唔起人住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）"},{"pid":"cd0bc1d40d5e6c79a50bb791c4d6f30ed0eef38c","tid":344023,"uid":68496,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T04:34:54.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"d4c768c57f47